data.description: Nice home located in popular subdivision with direct access to Loop 1604! Culdesac location* 3 car garage* 9 ft Ceilings, 18X18 tile floor in all wet areas* new laminate flooring downstairs & staircase* new carpets in bedrooms/upstairs* spacious remodeled kitchen with new white cabinetry, granite countertops, subway tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances (including fridge!)* recessed lighting, large pantry with spice rack* large living area & breakfast nook opens to the beautiful, covered, large wood deck in backyard.  Northside schools, zoned for Brennan HS* Elementary school is in neighborhood* Community pool & park* Close to shopping, entertainment, and major employers in the area - including Lackland AFB.
